OL,5,Ctargeted by a far-right sniper
OL,6, For nearly three weeks Belgium's
OL,7, leading virologist has been living in a
OL,8, safehouse with his wife and 12-year-old
OL,9, son, guarded by security agents.
OL,11,FWhile scientists across the world have
OL,12,Fcome under attack throughout the
OL,13,Fpandemic, the threat to Prof Marc Van
OL,14,FRanst is more serious than most.
OL,17,F"The threat was very real," Prof Van
OL,18,FRanst tells me from his safehouse, as
OL,19,Fhe relives the night he and his family
OL,20,Fwere moved into hiding on 18 May.
